
Ranger Help for: strip
======================

SYNTAX:      strip <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   10
BASE SP:     50 sp
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to attempt to strip an opponent's weapon from
them. Both of the Ranger's hands must be free in order to strip the 
weapon away. If the target is wielding two weapons, only one will be
stripped and which one you strip is random, depending on which one the
Ranger gets his or her hands on first.

